target.message:
hg commands required cwd=os.path.split(path)[0] (subprocess was being run from
runmanager directory).
set correct dtype for raw_output of static outputs
readded code to deal with single values

Added function print_time() which was used by pulse() but didn't exist (possibly comes from Monash Spinor lab?)
Fixed line in pulse function to use new print_time function
Use new print_time function for verbose markers printing
Added Shutter open_state to the connection_table_properties
Fixed compilation errors for clocklines with no Outputs

It turned out that many parameters are passed "by keyword" even if they
are not keyword arguments in the function signature.  Updated decorator
to ignore those.  Fixed error based on order of calling parent init in camera
Fixed variable name typo (trunc should've been truncation) in exp_ramp_t.
fixed minor bug causing Exception to not be raised properly
added checks for collision of instructions with ramps
